data.value: 安裝 Shadowsock 为 HND 型号
data.action: cd /tmp && wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hq450/fancyss/master/fancyss_hnd/shadowsocks.tar.gz && tar -zxvf /tmp/shadowsocks.tar.gz && chmod +x /tmp/shadowsocks/install.sh && sh /tmp/shadowsocks/install.sh && exit
